title: Register for the first Search Central Virtual Unconference Japan 2022!
description:
The Search Central Virtual Unconference Japan 2022 is now open for registration. The sessions
      will be conducted in Japanese. If you are interested, be sure to register by March 30! On top
      of that,the global Search Central Unconference 2022 is scheduled for April 27. Come meet the
      community, exchange ideas, and have fun together.
